    <author>
      <name>gregorw</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/12545</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Here is the answer that I've got from SAP Support:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;"Note 2447593 has moved to the sap help portal and is linked from the API Hub:&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/0f69f8fb28ac4bf48d2b57b9637e81fa/2cf48091d5864284ac4541b86a8737fd.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/0f69f8fb28ac4bf48d2b57b9637e81fa/2cf48091d5864284ac4541b86a8737fd.html&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Both APIs that you listed (&lt;SPAN&gt;BAPI_INQUIRY_CREATEFROMDATA2 and BAPI_QUOTATION_CREATEFROMDATA2&lt;/SPAN&gt;) are not mentioned in this document, thus you cannot use them in S/4HANA Public Cloud. For requesting any kind of API we offer the corresponding customer influence channel at&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://influence.sap.com/sap/ino/#/campaign/1175" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition for Extensibility and Integration (Remote APIs)&lt;/A&gt;, see also&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://api.sap.com/products/SAPS4HANACloud/overview" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://api.sap.com/products/SAPS4HANACloud/overview&lt;/A&gt;. This also replaces note 2653671."&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-blogs-by-sap/calling-bapis-in-the-sap-s-4hana-public-cloud/bc-p/13985564#M59209"/>
    <published>2025-01-14T22:41:37.646000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
